Ozem-Inspired (Combat)			KEY:Trait ~ Ozem-Inspired			NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Ozem-Inspired]			DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Tales of the Knights of Ozem have inspired you since childhood to lash out ref lexively against the undead. You gain a +1 trait bonus on attack rolls and damage rolls when making attacks of opportunity against undead. While you wield a shield, your shield bonus to AC improves by 1 against attacks of opportunity made by undead.		SOURCEPAGE:p.4
Blackjacket Weapon Flair (Combat)	KEY:Trait ~ Blackjacket Weapon Flair	NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Blackjacket Weapon Flair]	DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You trained with the Blackjackets of Druma to make optimal use of magic weapons. Whenever you roll a natural 20 (the die shows a "20") on a combat maneuver check with a magic weapon, you gain a +5 trait bonus on the check.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.4
Thunder and Fang Performer (Combat)	KEY:Trait ~ Thunder and Fang Performer				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Thunder and Fang Performer]	DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You learned from Shoanti champions to take advantage of the dramatic swings required by heavy weapons like the earth breaker. You gain a +2 trait bonus on Intimidate checks while wielding a two-handed melee weapon.																					SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Performer's Surprise (Combat)		KEY:Trait ~ Performer's Surprise					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Performer's Surprise]		DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You are practiced at the surprising combat tricks of Varisian wanderers. Against foes denied their Dexterity bonus to AC, you gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls with improvised weapons, exotic weapons, and thrown weapons.																			SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Monk Weapon Skill (Combat)		KEY:Trait ~ Monk Weapon Skill						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Monk Weapon Skill]		DESCISPI:YES	DESC:Your exposure to teaching from the Houses of Perfection makes your attacks with monk weapons even more deadly. Select one monk weapon with which you are proficient (unarmed attacks do not qualify for this purpose). You gain a +1 trait bonus on damage rolls with this weapon.											SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Merciful Scimitar (Combat)		KEY:Trait ~ Merciful Scimitar						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Merciful Scimitar]		DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You learned from worshipers of Sarenrae to cut foes with a scimitar without killing them. You can deal nonlethal damage with a scimitar without taking a penalty on your attack rolls.																										SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Red Mantis Bleeding (Combat)		KEY:Trait ~ Red Mantis Bleeding		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Red Mantis Bleeding]		DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You witnessed the training of Red Mantis assassins, either as a child on Mediogalti Island or as an aspirant, and learned to leave bleeding wounds. Whenever you confirm a critical hit with a slashing weapon, you also deal 1 point of bleed damage.																SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Roving Range (Combat)			KEY:Trait ~ Roving Range						CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Roving Range]						DESC:You learned from pirates to make the most of ranged attacks as you close with targets. Increase the range increment of ranged weapons (but not thrown weapons) you wield by 5 feet.																											SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Armed Grit (Combat)			KEY:Trait ~ Armed Grit							CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Armed Grit]						DESC:You make an impression during a standoff. As long as you have a firearm drawn, you gain a +2 trait bonus on saving throws against fear and the DCs of Intimidate checks to demoralize you increase by 2.																							SOURCEPAGE:p.5
Ichimeiyo Champion (Combat)		KEY:Trait ~ Ichimeiyo Champion		NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Trait.BasicTrait.CombatTrait	PREMULT:1,[PREVAREQ:BypassTraitRestriction,1],[!PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,TYPE.CombatTrait],[PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Trait ~ Ichimeiyo Champion]		DESCISPI:YES	DESC:You draw strength from adhering to the Ichimeiyo honor code in combat. Once per day, if an effect would compel you to harm an ally, abandon an ally, or break your word, you can attempt a Will save at the usual DC to end the effect. If the effect normally allows a Will save at this point, you can roll twice and take the better result.	SOURCEPAGE:p.5

