type_KipUpDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_Archetype_BleedingWoundDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_Archetype_PerfectThrustDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_Archetype_CharmedLife|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_CF_DerringDoDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_CF_KipUpDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_CF_BleedingWoundDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_CF_PerfectThrustDeed|true	FACT:Swashbuckler_CF_CharmedLife|true
