Martial Flexibility			KEY:Varisian Free-Style Fighter ~ Martial Flexibility								NAMEISPI:YES	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:Fighter Class Feature.Varisian Free-Style Fighter Class Feature.SpecialQuality.Extraordinary																																																																																									DEFINE:FreeStyleFighterMartialFlexibilityTimes|0	DEFINE:FreeStyleFighterMartialFlexibilityLVL|0	DEFINE:Active_FreeStyle_Martial_Flexibility|0	DESCISPI:YES	DESC:A Varisian free-style fighter can take a move action to gain the benefit of a combat feat she doesn't possess.|!PRECLASS:1,Fighter=6	DESC:A Varisian free-style fighter can use this ability to gain the benefit of two combat feats at the same time. She may select one feat as a swift action or two feats as a move action.|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=6|!PRECLASS:1,Fighter=10	DESC:A Varisian free-style fighter can use this ability to gain the benefit of three combat feats at the same time. She may select one feat as a free action, two feats as a swift action, or three feats as a move action.|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=10|!PRECLASS:1,Fighter=12	DESC:A Varisian free-style fighter can use this ability to gain the benefit of one combat feat as an immediate action or three combat feats as a swift action.|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=12|!PRECLASS:1,Fighter=20	DESC:A Varisian free-style fighter can use this ability to gain the benefit of any number of combat feats as a swift action.|PRECLASS:1,Fighter=20	DESC:This effect lasts for 1 minute. The Varisian free-style fighter must meet all the feat's prerequisites. She may use this ability %1 times per day. The Varisian free-style fighter can use this ability again before the duration expires in order to replace the previous combat feat with another choice. If a combat feat has a daily use limitation (such as Stunning Fist), any uses of that combat feat while using this ability count toward that feat's daily limit.|FreeStyleFighterMartialFlexibilityTimes																ABILITY:Internal|AUTOMATIC|Free-